title: Google\Cloud\AIPlatform\V1\BatchPredictionJob\OutputInfo
name: OutputInfo
description:
Further describes this job's output.

Supplements [output_config][google.cloud.aiplatform.v1.BatchPredictionJob.output_config].

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.aiplatform.v1.BatchPredictionJob.OutputInfo

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.gcs_output_directory
params.description: Output only. The full path of the Cloud Storage directory created, into which the prediction output is written.

params.name: data.bigquery_output_dataset
params.description: Output only. The path of the BigQuery dataset created, in bq://projectId.bqDatasetId format, into which the prediction output is written.

params.name: data.bigquery_output_table
params.description: Output only. The name of the BigQuery table created, in predictions_<timestamp> format, into which the prediction output is written. Can be used by UI to generate the BigQuery output path, for example.
